{"tid":1171954,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"話通過引渡法外資走洒既人有咩理據？","createTime":"2019-05-26T05:39:10.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-26T15:42:39.000Z","uid":89861,"like":7,"dislike":108,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"01de59b61dd29d3188f07fd78bafa3373cd14338","tid":1171954,"uid":89861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:39:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://gbtimes.com/china-remains-second-largest-fdi-recipient-in-the-world\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fgbtimes.com%2Fchina-remains-second-largest-fdi-recipient-in-the-world&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=a6e531bb\" target=\"_blank\">https://gbtimes.com/china-remains-second-largest-fdi-recipient-in-the-world</a><br />\n<br />\n中國引進外資額連續幾年排第二，緊次於美國，<br />\n引渡法搞外資反而唔敢投資香港？<br />\n<br />\n或者有既，所謂外資即係d中國貪官唔會再投資香港既地產保險 ，搞到樓會跌囉"},{"pid":"b4f09ae15cc1392f9169a571d165173e1d223ad4","tid":1171954,"uid":123969,"like":38,"dislike":2,"score":36,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T05:46:39.000Z","msg":"香港吸引外資嘅主要係金融同外匯產品<br />\n健全嘅金融體制要基於健全嘅法治體制先會得到保障<br />\n大陸投資應該多數都係生產<br />\n法治要求相對冇咁高 最緊要就係夠平<br />\n<br />\n香港於2017年吸納的直接外來投資達1,040億美元，全球排第三位，亞洲排名僅次於中國(1,360億美元)。<br />\n<br />\n自己諗下啲錢去咗邊"},{"pid":"ce6da00ba783d81a4ba6e87d1ab19d75d7a04d6c","tid":1171954,"uid":50457,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-26T06:00:20.000Z","msg":"改革開放至今　港佔內地外資五成<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181127/20555625\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181127%2F20555625&d=mZhSvp2BRS%2BtHw05K%2FyMFFe0bVP%2BLlUkdLfYKyPPBhg%3D&h=dcf185de\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181127%2F20555625&h=f13ae2d6\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181127/20555625</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知個報告係咪當香港資金為外資，正所謂中國發展，香